<!Doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Bootstrap demo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="~/css/StoryListingPage.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-fluid p-0">
        <div class="upper-image">
            <img class="w-100" src="~/images/Grow-Trees-On-the-path-to-environment-sustainability-login.png" />
            <div class="centered">
                <div class="centered-txt">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent interdum tempus ligula, nec malesuada diam maximus sit amet. Aliquam auctor euismod tellus, eget posuere odio fringilla id.
                </div>
                <div class="btn share-story-btn mt-2">
                    Share your story <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="container story-list">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="~/images/Grow-Trees-On-the-path-to-environment-sustainability-2.png" />
                    <div class="centered story-detail-btn ">
                        <a class="btn view-story-btn mt-2">
                            View Details <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="theme-tag container-fluid">
                    Environment
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">
                        10 User and Customer Engagement Strategies for 2019
                    </h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec vulputate elementum accumsan. Quisque aliquam risus.
                    </p>

                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <img class="story-volunteer" src="~/images/volunteer1.png"> Volunteer name</img>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


